infectious /ɪnˈfɛkʃəs/

1. ADJ A disease that is infectious can be caught by being near a person who has it. Compare . 传染的 

例： ...infectious diseases such as measles. …像麻疹这样的传染病。 

2. ADJ If a feeling is infectious , it spreads to other people. 有感染力的 

例： She radiates an infectious enthusiasm for everything she does. 她做的每件事都散发出一种有感染力的热情。

</div>

